OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 1 JUN
OL,4,G1125FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAlistair and Emma host at their
OL,6,     Gfour-star Castle Hill Guesthouse
OL,7,     Gin sleepy Lynton, north Devon.
OL,8,     GThe group activity requires a
OL,9,     Ghead for heights, and Mrs Tee
OL,10,     Gproves hard to please.
OL,11,G1155FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe competition heads north to
OL,13,     Gthe three-star Vidella in
OL,14,     GBlackpool, run by fun-loving
OL,15,     Gpranksters John and Neil, who
OL,16,     Ghave hatched a plan to pay back
OL,17,     GAlistair for hating their home
OL,18,     Gtown.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
