OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 1 JUN
OL,4,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe group check in to the
OL,6,     Gboutique Urban Beach B&B in
OL,7,     GBournemouth, with its mod cons
OL,8,     Gand deluxe bathrooms. And host
OL,9,     GMark treats his guests to a
OL,10,     Gspeedboat ride along the Jurassic
OL,11,     GCoast.
OL,12,G1300FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe B&Bers meet for one last time
OL,14,     Gto find out how much they've been
OL,15,     Gpaid and to thrash out their
OL,16,     Gdifferences. There's trouble as
OL,17,     GMrs Tee and Alistair and Emma
OL,18,     Gclash over their scores.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
