OL,4,G1435FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GPeterborough. Mobile hairdresser
OL,6,     GBen plans a gourmet night, as he
OL,7,     Gentertains his guests with his
OL,8,     Gamazing body art, cooking skills
OL,9,     Gand pet crabs.
OL,10,G1510FCome Dine with Me
OL,11,     GPeterborough. Fridge salesman
OL,12,     GGregory serves up a Spanish menu
OL,13,     Gand a charm offensive.
OL,14,G1540FCome Dine with Me
OL,15,     GPeterborough. Rosie has ruffled
OL,16,     Gfeathers all week. Now it's her
OL,17,     Gguests' turn to scour every
OL,18,     Gelement of her Brazilian night,
OL,19,     Gfrom the samba dancers to her
OL,20,     Gauthentic pig-ear stew.
