OL,4,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe competition kicks off at
OL,6,     GAnstey Hall in Cambridge, where
OL,7,     Gfather and son John and Johnny de
OL,8,     GBruyne hope to impress their
OL,9,     Gguests with an afternoon of goose
OL,10,     Gherding and a formal dinner.
OL,11,G1650FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe second visit is to the
OL,13,     Gclothes-free Clover Spa and Hotel
OL,14,     Gin Birmingham, where owner Tim
OL,15,     GHiggs plans to convert his rivals
OL,16,     Gto the joys of naturism.
