OL,4,G1720FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GMark Davidson and Layla Caton are
OL,6,     Gdetermined to deliver a heavenly
OL,7,     Gstay at The Angel Hotel in
OL,8,     GColeford, Gloucestershire. But
OL,9,     Gmanners slip over dinner and
OL,10,     Gthere's confusion at breakfast.
OL,11,G1750FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe final visit is to Higher
OL,13,     GGitcombe in Totnes, Devon, run by
OL,14,     GLynnie and Paul Jolly. But not
OL,15,     Geveryone is impressed by their
OL,16,     Gefforts to spoil their guests.
