OL,8,     GAnastasia, who's 80, has a severe
OL,9,     Gpain in her leg and is sent for
OL,10,     Gan X-ray.
OL,11,G2305F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics treat a woman who's
OL,13,     Gfallen headfirst through a glass
OL,14,     Gdoor and a man complaining of
OL,15,     Gcrushing headaches, and are
OL,16,     Gcalled out to a two-vehicle smash.
